      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"5. FOXY JAY was quickly into stride and burnt early from out wide where she gave a sight, finishing second (22.14) and beaten 1.75 lengths over 390m at this track. Can go on with it. 3. PAW REVY stalked the lead after a clean break from the tricky draw and went on to finish second (22.21) at Ballarat in a R/A FIN over 390m. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Will give a great sight again. 1. PAW HADES looks close to another win after finishing third last time (22.24) at Ballarat. Leading player again. 4. CINNABAR ICON should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.\",\"runners\":[5,3,1,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
